name: Listened to Dear Internet Episode 26 – Foodie Fraud

content.html:
Dear Internet, This week’s show we dive into the world of meat crimes and foodie fraud. How do you deal with a spouse running away with your dogs? Who put all this meat in here? And why are these brownies so good. Thank you for reading this, XOXO We are a new show, and would greatly appreciate if you could leave us a 5-star review on your podcast app of choice! If you want more Dear Internet, please consider supporting us on patreon through Dear Internet. Sincerely, The coHosts- Nick Bristow, Jennifer Cheek, Michael DiMauro, and Tim Lanning! Apple Podcast, Spotify, RSS – follow us on Twitter!

By Dear Internet
